{"tid":369393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"農歷七月就立刻發生左怪事","createTime":"2017-08-22T09:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T11:06:51.000Z","uid":39906,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0998a8f98befdf25825833c295545ae49002c78","tid":369393,"uid":39906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"小弟今天發生左一個奇怪事件，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中午食完飯回公司，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見食完飯仲有啲時間，<br />\n用公司部電腦去HKTV看下今天有咩電子特賣，<br />\n一去到個網，<br />\n就見到個購物車有12樣東西，<br />\n我又無買野 點解會有12樣東西呢，<br />\n咁就按入購物車睇下啦，<br />\n見到個地址唔同左既。<br />\n唔係送去我平時送開個地址喎，<br />\n唔通比人Hack左我ACC，<br />\n按返去主頁看多次，<br />\n購物車變左做13樣。<br />\n巧驚驚，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來發覺個ACC，唔係本人。<br />\n係一個唔識既人。<br />\n<br />\nPS 無人用過我部機，同公司冇IT既。<br />\n啊仲有 MAC機來既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b50556bb6fe227462e2e042a8d2103e8168d97","tid":369393,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:51:11.000Z","msg":"你應該去hktv到屌鳩佢"},{"pid":"c0ebe7d965164347861e028b96f2656bbfaa5bb5","tid":369393,"uid":39906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T10:12:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你應該去hktv到屌鳩佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問左佢啦 <br />\n<br />\n佢話冇可能<br />\n<br />\n話問吓IT喎<br />\n<br />\n之後就CUT左我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c1f59faf22dc07ee4ba50cb358553547635a7f","tid":369393,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T10:40:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嘩<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n有鬼啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 